text: Saint George is one of Dominica's 10 administrative parishes. ==Roseau== The capital city of Dominica, Roseau, is in this parish, as well as its suburbs: *Bath Estate *Elmshall *Kings Hill *Copthall *Newtown (once Charlotteville) *Castle Comfort *Goodwill *Potters Ville *Stock Farm *Tarish Pit *Yam Piece *Belle Vue Rawle *Fond Col√© ==References== Category:Parishes of Dominica
title: Saint George Parish, Dominica
